Package org.variantsync.diffdetective.diff

Class Lines

java.lang.Object
org.variantsync.diffdetective.diff.Lines
public class Lines extends Object
Class to hold a range of line numbers. Mainly used to locate code snippets in source code files and textual diffs.
Author:
Paul Bittner
